571
00:28:58,980 --> 00:29:00,350
To keep the heavenly fire burning,

572
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:03,370
the Divine Hand must also serve as fuel.

573
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:05,200
As the saying goes,

574
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:08,590
if I don't enter hell, who will?

575
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:32,630
You actually want to use the Divine Left Hand

576
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,200
to destroy this world?

577
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:36,230
I won't destroy this world.

578
00:29:37,180 --> 00:29:39,420
I'll merely cleanse it with heavenly fire.

579
00:29:40,810 --> 00:29:41,980
You've become a demon.

580
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:42,850
Become a demon?

581
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:58,430
I heard you want to devour me.

582
00:30:07,170 --> 00:30:08,960
Oh no, I can't hold it back anymore.

583
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:09,750
Hold on.

584
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:10,890
Yuanzhong hasn't woken up yet.

585
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,840
Do you think I don't want to hold on?

586
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:18,400
Yuanzhong.

587
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,440
You're alright now?

588
00:30:19,730 --> 00:30:20,900
I was fine all along.

589
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,270
I originally wanted to let you

590
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,510
live a bit longer,

591
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:37,110
but you're seeking your own death.

592
00:30:37,970 --> 00:30:39,490
So don't blame me.

593
00:31:49,610 --> 00:31:50,190
Come in.

594
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:03,270
You're awake.

595
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,520
Is everything alright?

596
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:09,310
It feels like I've had a long dream,

597
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:10,110
but I can't remember

598
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:11,640
what happened in the dream.

599
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,510
The matters here are settled.

600
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:15,070
Are you willing

601
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,590
to continue to Yandu with me?

602
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:18,640
Of course.

603
00:32:18,830 --> 00:32:19,640
Really?

604
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,000
Yuanzhong,

605
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:25,640
my life, death, honor, and disgrace are all tied to you.

606
00:32:26,170 --> 00:32:27,810
I will naturally put you first in everything.

607
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,440
Besides, we made

608
00:32:29,600 --> 00:32:31,120
that decision together.

609
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,310
Then let's pack up

610
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:35,960
and set off immediately.

611
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:36,960
Alright.

612
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:39,130
Yunniang, you're here.

613
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:46,790
Miss Ji,

614
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:48,350
I'm here to see Pei Jiu.

615
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:49,590
Is he inside?

616
00:32:51,130 --> 00:32:51,930
He…

617
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:58,860
I'm here. What's the matter?

618
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:33,510
I'm wearing a hairpin today.

619
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:38,610
It was given by you.

620
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,720
It was given by Pei Jiu.

621
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,270
Why are you in such a hurry

622
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,550
to distance yourself from me?

623
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,480
We were just passing acquaintances.

624
00:33:48,030 --> 00:33:49,240
There was never any relationship.

625
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:51,030
I won't interfere with Pei Jiu's life,

626
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,240
and as for my life,

627
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:54,310
I hope he can do the same.

628
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:57,880
Just passing acquaintances?

629
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,160
You've really changed into a different person.

630
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:07,680
You left

631
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:09,070
this with me.

632
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,840
You were worried you might forget,

633
00:34:12,330 --> 00:34:13,790
so you specifically instructed me

634
00:34:14,850 --> 00:34:16,520
to make sure I handed it to you personally.

635
00:34:25,510 --> 00:34:26,630
In Pei Jiu's notebook,

636
00:34:26,630 --> 00:34:27,510
there are many records

637
00:34:27,510 --> 00:34:28,840
of his past with Yunniang.

638
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,960
After Lu Chen reads it,

639
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,590
he'll be swayed, right?

640
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,280
It's only human nature.

641
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:38,000
But what if

642
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,360
he decides not to go with you?

643
00:34:43,070 --> 00:34:44,190
He won't read it.

644
00:35:04,690 --> 00:35:05,920
My name is Lu Chen.

645
00:35:06,890 --> 00:35:08,410
I'm one of the weapon spirits

646
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,510
of the Youhu Clan's High Priest.

647
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:11,230
Due to certain circumstances,

648
00:35:11,510 --> 00:35:13,030
I had forgotten my past

649
00:35:13,590 --> 00:35:14,880
and was in a daze for over 10 years.

650
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,190
You took care of me.

651
00:35:18,710 --> 00:35:20,400
But I'm not from Orange Lake.

652
00:35:21,070 --> 00:35:22,710
I have a past you don't know about

653
00:35:23,190 --> 00:35:24,800
and a future you don't understand.

654
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,710
I am not Pei Jiu.

655
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,670
This notebook and you

656
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,630
have nothing to do with me.

657
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:33,800
Do you understand?

658
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:38,000
I understand.

659
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:40,670
That's good.

660
00:35:41,670 --> 00:35:42,930
I'm about to leave this place.

661
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:45,670
Take care of yourself.

662
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:50,030
You too,

663
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:08,510
Mr. Lu Chen.

664
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,480
Pei Jiu won't come back anymore,

665
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:15,070
will he?

666
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:22,150
No, he won't.

667
00:36:57,190 --> 00:36:58,190
I'll go out and have a look.

668
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:15,030
Do you really not remember anything?

669
00:37:15,670 --> 00:37:16,760
Though the dream was beautiful,

670
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:18,760
it was nothing more than an illusion.

671
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,280
Now that I've awakened, my original intention remains unchanged.

672
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:22,960
There are more important things

673
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:23,920
waiting for me to do.

674
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:40,630
Lu Chen is still Lu Chen.

675
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,810
Is Yuanzhong still Yuanzhong?

676
00:37:47,030 --> 00:37:47,840
Of course.

677
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:49,670
That's good.

678
00:37:59,690 --> 00:38:05,280
[Orange Lake]

679
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:02,670
Immortal elders,

680
00:38:05,670 --> 00:38:07,880
the villagers of Orange Lake have gathered

681
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:11,550
to wish you a safe journey.

682
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,070
Have a safe journey.

683
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,590
Why must Lu Chen

684
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:34,800
come with us?

685
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:37,230
Although he's a weapon spirit,

686
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,920
he has long since developed consciousness

687
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,590
and become an independent individual.

688
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:42,400
Can't we let him

689
00:38:42,420 --> 00:38:44,300
choose based on his own preferences?

690
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,190
This is the path he has chosen.

691
00:38:46,630 --> 00:38:47,920
You're only considering it

692
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,800
from Pei Jiu's perspective.

693
00:38:49,250 --> 00:38:50,850
Why not consider Lu Chen's perspective?

694
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,280
Because

695
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,400
at least Pei Jiu

696
00:38:57,870 --> 00:38:59,750
was much happier than Lu Chen.

