♫Fearlessly roaming across the world♫

721
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:20,010
[Pei Jiu loves Yunniang]

722
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:24,190
Who will win in the end?

723
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,070
Come on,

724
00:41:25,070 --> 00:41:26,030
let's do it again.

725
00:41:26,230 --> 00:41:27,030
Come on, come on.

726
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:28,000
I'm four.

727
00:41:29,550 --> 00:41:30,360
No, no, no.

728
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:31,070
I didn't call it out.

729
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:32,280
Zi Fei, hurry up and try again.

730
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,070
You—

731
00:41:33,070 --> 00:41:35,110
Come on, come on.

732
00:41:35,110 --> 00:41:35,960
I-I didn't call it out again.

733
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,630
Hey, how can you cheat like that?

734
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:40,320
When will they finish?

735
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:43,480
Zi Fei has terrible luck in gambling.

736
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:46,230
It'll be a while before he wins.

737
00:41:48,030 --> 00:41:48,840
So where are we

738
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:49,800
going next?

739
00:41:50,710 --> 00:41:51,920
For the remaining two seals,

740
00:41:52,110 --> 00:41:53,230
one is in Yandu

741
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,280
and the other is in the middle of Su River.

742
00:41:55,670 --> 00:41:58,000
I've heard that Yandu is the city of craftsmanship

743
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,070
and is very prosperous.

744
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,400
The markets there are filled with precious goods,

745
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:03,550
houses are full of fine silks, and carriages stream like water.

746
00:42:03,600 --> 00:42:04,410
Even at night,

747
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:05,550
there's music and dancing,

748
00:42:05,550 --> 00:42:06,550
and the lights never go out.

749
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:08,510
Zi Fei is so eager to win.

750
00:42:08,710 --> 00:42:10,110
Could it be because if he wins,

751
00:42:10,110 --> 00:42:11,400
he can go to Yandu?

752
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:14,630
No, he wants to go to Su River.

753
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,110
Su River?

754
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:18,480
That place is remote.

755
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:20,550
It's far away and sparsely populated.

756
00:42:20,590 --> 00:42:22,150
Why would he want to go there?

757
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,590
You lost this time, didn't you?

758
00:42:23,710 --> 00:42:25,070
It doesn't count. You were too slow.

759
00:42:25,070 --> 00:42:25,670
Let's do it again, come on.

760
00:42:25,670 --> 00:42:26,590
It doesn't count again?

761
00:42:26,590 --> 00:42:27,840
You're just a sore loser.

762
00:42:28,110 --> 00:42:28,920
Yes,

763
00:42:29,190 --> 00:42:30,670
I just want to go to Su River

764
00:42:30,670 --> 00:42:31,670
to bring Ling Yao out.

765
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:33,110
You and Lu Chen can accompany them to Yandu,

766
00:42:33,110 --> 00:42:34,320
and that's that!

767
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:35,800
What do you mean?

768
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:36,510
No way.

769
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:38,440
I want to go to Su River to pick up Ling Yao too.

770
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:43,030
With your dull appearance,

771
00:42:43,030 --> 00:42:44,150
do you think she would like you?

772
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:45,590
What are you going there for?

773
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:46,880
Nonsense!

774
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,880
Ling Yao likes me very much.

775
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,880
Ling Yao is a woman?

776
00:42:55,150 --> 00:42:56,590
A beautiful woman.
